high_descs: Move to the right to face the counter top to the right of the sink.
Pick the napkin up from off of the counter.
Move to to the left to face the sink.
Place the napkin in the sink, run the water over the napkin, turn off the water off and pick up the napkin.
Turn around and walk straight to stand next to the right of the toilet.
Place the napkin on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place the wet napkin on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: walk to the right to face the bathroom sink
pick up the red handkerchief on the right side of the counter next to the sink
walk to the left to face the full bathroom sink
put the handkerchief in the sink basin, wash it with water, pick it up from the sink basin
walk to the toilet on the right side, turn and face the right side of the toilet
put the handkerchief on the toilet tank top in front of the other red handkerchief
anns.task_desc: wash a handkerchief to put on the toilet tank

high_descs: Walk straight and face the sink.
Grab the dirty red cloth off of the sink.
Rinse the cloth off in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Place the clean cloth on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean cloth on top of the toilet.
